
```bash
systemctl start datadog-agent
```


```bash
datadog-agent status
```

```bash
datadog-agent configcheck
```

[config](https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-agent/blob/main/pkg/config/config_template.yaml)

```bash
datadog-agent config  
```


```bash
root@agent-host:~/lab# datadog-agent config|grep ^env
env: agent-host-lab
root@agent-host:~/lab# env |grep DD_ENV
DD_ENV=agent-host-lab
```

```bash
cat /etc/datadog-agent/datadog.yaml
```

```bash
systemctl restart datadog-agent
```